CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper January 24, 1953, pg. 30, reads: "Celebration of YMCA Week Starts This Saturday - The Playdels... a teen-age club which is affiliated with the boys' department. They are sponsored by Emma Lou, the popular disc jockey. The youngsters like to have this smart group of young ladies around. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five young women in "Playdels" club, including one seated on left wearing sweater with "M" monogram, gathered in Centre Avenue YMCA
